{"tid":1308044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪應該放棄連儂牆？","createTime":"2019-07-11T19:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:21:32.000Z","uid":40287,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"eae76952d7e70223ac5f9260eae9de0c8c9c5e50","tid":1308044,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:19:24.000Z","msg":"保留返政總嗰個或者兩三個就算，因為呢幾日開始多暴力藍絲睇到任打唔嬲走去打人，啲片令佢哋士氣大增，而且下下要出去幫拖嘅，好多巴絲打都好攰，唔係話向惡勢力低頭，但咁樣長期消耗真係會影響埋其他支線及主線。<br />\n<br />\n不如真係好似有啲巴打絲打咁建議，唔好花太多精力去連儂牆嗰度，咁樣盞愈嚟愈多人受傷，只會重覆返2014年嘅事。"},{"pid":"3d3ae7cde9c87b21b4405ea241d1b3fa29dd35b3","tid":1308044,"uid":167177,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:29:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔轉做快閃連儂牆？"},{"pid":"9574ac0c4121737144da338479bb3c545e624889","tid":1308044,"uid":71085,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:30:25.000Z","msg":"撕一貼十你覺得只係口號？"},{"pid":"81d5c5b10ab06c552dca90c726022d991a37043e","tid":1308044,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:31:16.000Z","msg":"應該放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係一定有班左膠覺得比廢老打搶到民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實死攬啲廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129019f5360be07ca58c691bbce6df2bf04df6d9","tid":1308044,"uid":60432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:32:11.000Z","msg":"2019年喇，藍絲邊會睇連儂牆<br />\n反而長輩圖仲多人睇仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1065c0aa1ff5860233f6166a96acfb469ff8f4fa","tid":1308044,"uid":167177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:33:53.000Z","msg":"轉貼大量海報，例如毛澤東底，字印 &quot;革命無眾，造反有理！&quot;等幫助宣傳學生運動字句，然後一排排貼去牆。"},{"pid":"0f09e1370cb086931a8cee985f5a6aa96ab3bb94","tid":1308044,"uid":88743,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x