8afb09f077ce6c4b82ae6bd9262b8469451","tid":1308044,"uid":235986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:58:22.000Z","msg":"獨立調查呢？"},{"pid":"ea4d1b12032bb4e715a1bc0a2d1883968ebe7f42","tid":1308044,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:01:13.000Z","msg":"可以整既<br />\n但唔好晒時間守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401ece3737269911113a8e51d25e99158953f82d","tid":1308044,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:03:45.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9bf3bd73a3d1b549fcf7cf0d998b5ea09caa30d","tid":1308044,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"其實守唔係唔得<br />\n但係要揀幾個標誌性嘅黎守<br />\n好似大埔呢啲"},{"pid":"173ef3f8c2e9e9a1b7e1e275d39a082e60e0d776","tid":1308044,"uid":217383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d3ae7cde9c87b21b4405ea241d1b3fa29dd35b3","tid":1308044,"uid":167177,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:29:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔轉做快閃連儂牆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:08:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以試下<br />\n例如唔好貼死一個地方 你搭下巴士貼一兩張<br />\n行行下心血來潮又貼一兩張<br />\n啲藍c想met走曬都難 分得太散<br />\n依家有個區啲藍c就守係個邊打人 咁樣好冒險"},{"pid":"816f443c9eee7af07688d3650d39735b3129c72f","tid":1308044,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"連農牆係好，但冇必要成日為守塊牆而開晒post call馬<br />\n咁樣只會消耗義士意志<br />\n比人撕，咪一陣再貼過囉"},{"pid":"2ee6f17c170df8198ab84c1acd52aabb3a189971","tid":1308044,"uid":182406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布： 遊行，集會，圍堵先係主線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308079</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}